high_descs: Turn around and cross the room, then hang right and walk to the microwave
Pick up the furthest most tomato, the one right next to the paper towel roll
Turn right and take a step then turn left toward the microwave.
Place the tomato in the microwave behind the right hand green cup then close the microwave and turn it on.  Open the microwave and pick up the tomato then close the microwave
Take a step to the left
Place the tomato on the microwave stand near the left corner closest to you
anns.task_desc: Place a cooked tomato on a microwave stand

high_descs: Turn around and walk to the microwave on the right.
Take a tomato next to the microwave.
Turn right then turn left and walk to the microwave.
Open the door, put the tomato inside, close the door, and turn the microwave on. Remove the tomato when it's done and close the door.
Turn left then turn right and walk to the microwave.
Place the tomato back on the counter next to the microwave.
anns.task_desc: Place a microwave tomato on the counter.

high_descs: Turn around and stand in front of the microwave.
Pick the tomato up from behind the other tomato.
Move to the right and stand in front of the microwave.
Put the tomato in the microwave, turn it on, and then take the tomato out and shut the door.
Move to the left and stand on the left side of the microwave.
Put the tomato down next to the other one.
anns.task_desc: Put a heated tomato on the counter.
